due out in September.<p><a href=\"http://games.slashdot.org/story/09/07/14/1610208/emAionem-Shaping-Up-For-US-Launch?from=rss\"><img src=\"http://slashdot.org/slashdot-it.pl?from=rss&amp;op=image&amp;style=h0&amp;sid=09/07/14/1610208\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://games.slashdot.org/story/09/07/14/1610208/emAionem-Shaping-Up-For-US-Launch?from=rss\">Read more of this story</a> at Slashdot.</p>
