ies should simply stop paying one, relying on the old argument about promotion.\"<p><a href=\"http://yro.slashdot.org/story/09/07/13/2243233/Pandora-Wants-Radio-Stations-To-Pay-For-Music-Too?from=rss\"><img src=\"http://slashdot.org/slashdot-it.pl?from=rss&amp;op=image&amp;style=h0&amp;sid=09/07/13/2243233\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://yro.slashdot.org/story/09/07/13/2243233/Pandora-Wants-Radio-Stations-To-Pay-For-Music-Too?from=rss\">Read more of this story</a> at Slashdot.</p>
